Neva Gerber https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neva_Gerber 0 Genevieve Dolores Gerber (April 3, 1894 – January 2, 1974) was an American silent film actress who appeared in 128 films between 1912 and 1930. She used the name Jean Dolores in her last two films.
